# Innovation In Action

This repository captures how I translate cross-industry project, program, and portfolio leadership experience into practical innovation work. It is a living record of how I build, test, and evolve new capabilities — especially where technology, operating environments, and human systems intersect.

My focus is not on experimenting with tools for their own sake, but on designing approaches that can survive real organizational constraints: governance, risk, resource limits, stakeholder dynamics, and the need to prove value.

